@Node scr_cursrt()
scr_cursrt-Move cursor right one character

Synopsis

	#include <scrcntl.h>

	void scr_cursrt(void);       /* move cursor right one character */

Description

	This function moves the cursor right one character without
	modifying any characters.

	You can achieve the same functionality by printing standard ANSI
	X3.64 console control codes to the console window.

Portability

